name: HERE Data Lens REST API
description:
# HERE Data Lens
A data visualisation toolkit for rapidly developing applications on the world’s best map.
HERE Data Lens consists of 3 components that provide a seamless developer experience for quickly creating & deploying your data visualisations.
These are REST API, JS API and Data Lens Editor

## HERE Data Lens REST API
Services to store, query, filter, aggregate and transform millions of data rows in just milliseconds.

URL: [http://datalens.here.com/](http://datalens.here.com/)

External access: [https://developer.here.com/contact-us](https://developer.here.com/contact-us)

Internal access: ???

folders.name: 01. User Authentication
folders.description:
User Authentication is **required** by all the requests in this collection.

Obtain the account under the [https://account.here.com/](https://account.here.com/)

headers.name: Access-Control-Allow-Credentials
